This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video inpainting, which is a common task in computer vision. The use of alignment and attention modules also suggests a focus on visual processing. The paper may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with video data. The use of a feed-forward network suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of large spatial-temporal window sizes suggests a focus on graphics (cs.GR) as well.
